784
01:08:35,868 --> 01:08:37,871
Your Mother's alive.

785
01:08:41,627 --> 01:08:43,836
Please. Please.

786
01:08:43,972 --> 01:08:46,767
Where is she?

787
01:09:16,455 --> 01:09:17,974
Mom?

788
01:09:23,765 --> 01:09:25,354
Oh, my God.

789
01:09:35,696 --> 01:09:38,147
It's been so long.

790
01:09:44,110 --> 01:09:46,354
I knew, one day, that you'd
walk through that door.

791
01:09:51,317 --> 01:09:53,181
Oh, don't do that.

792
01:09:53,317 --> 01:09:56,630
No, don't be sad.

793
01:09:56,765 --> 01:10:00,354
Everything's
gonna be all right.

794
01:10:00,489 --> 01:10:03,561
I hate it
when you're sad.

795
01:10:05,903 --> 01:10:08,492
You remember how
Mama loves her baby.

796
01:10:10,868 --> 01:10:12,595
