a little backwards, didn't I?

806
01:14:02,455 --> 01:14:05,078
But see, my Mother
removed another screen.

807
01:14:05,213 --> 01:14:09,147
Now, everything's clear.

808
01:14:09,282 --> 01:14:12,526
I never hurt you.
