809
01:14:12,662 --> 01:14:14,561
It was her.

810
01:14:14,696 --> 01:14:17,112
You were worse than her.

811
01:14:17,248 --> 01:14:20,147
You let it happen.

812
01:14:20,282 --> 01:14:22,250
You left me alone with her.

813
01:14:24,075 --> 01:14:26,492
Come on. Let's play.

814
01:14:26,627 --> 01:14:30,009
Seth is five years old,

815
01:14:30,144 --> 01:14:33,836
you come home
and find his--

816
01:14:33,972 --> 01:14:36,940
his little head
in a bandage.

817
01:14:37,075 --> 01:14:39,319
What do you do?

818
01:14:39,455 --> 01:14:42,112
If you're gonna
kill me, do it now.

819
01:14:49,937 --> 01:14:52,043
Wrong answer.

820
01:14:52,179 --> 01:14:54,354
Sorry.

821
01:14:54,489 --> 01:14:56,354
