a little hint.

822
01:14:58,662 --> 01:15:00,423
You don't do Jack shit.

823
01:15:07,937 --> 01:15:09,802
Why didn't you do something?

824
01:15:09,937 --> 01:15:13,974
She said it was an accident.
That you slipped in the tub.

825
01:15:14,110 --> 01:15:16,733
I was out of the country.

826
01:15:16,868 --> 01:15:18,871
