849
01:16:36,800 --> 01:16:40,905
Hmm. Mama doesn't
need Daddy anyway.

850
01:16:43,006 --> 01:16:45,354
Mama only needs you.

851
01:16:50,213 --> 01:16:52,078
Mama loves her baby.

852
01:16:59,179 --> 01:17:03,354
When she was done...

853
01:17:03,489 --> 01:17:05,733
she said that
I made her do it.

854
01:17:05,868 --> 01:17:08,974
That I was dirty.

855
01:17:09,110 --> 01:17:10,836
I was filthy.

856
01:17:15,662 --> 01:17:17,871
It was my fault...

857
01:17:18,006 --> 01:17:20,181
that it happened.

858
01:17:25,627 --> 01:17:27,561
When she left,
I heard her lock my door.

859
01:17:27,696 --> 01:17:30,940
Mommy? Mommy?

860
01:17:31,075 --> 01:17:33,009
Mommy, I can't open the door.

861
01:17:35,075 --> 01:17:37,802
Mommy! Mommy!

862
01:18:03,144 --> 01:18:05,285
Come on. Hey.

863
01:18:05,420 --> 01:18:07,250
Don't-- don't be sad.

864
01:18:10,696 --> 01:18:12,492
I hate it when you're sad.

865
01:18:17,144 --> 01:18:18,802
Everything's gonna be fine.

866
01:18:20,110 --> 01:18:22,147
Mama loves her baby.

867
01:18:22,282 --> 01:18:24,181
Mama loves her baby.

868
01:18:30,868 --> 01:18:32,940
