869
01:18:33,075 --> 01:18:35,009
he's dirty.

870
01:18:35,144 --> 01:18:38,630
He's filthy,

871
01:18:38,765 --> 01:18:41,388
and he should have
died in that fire.

872
01:18:46,282 --> 01:18:47,905
What did you say?

873
01:18:50,972 --> 01:18:52,802
Huh?

874
01:18:54,834 --> 01:18:55,836
I love you.

875
01:19:52,834 --> 01:19:57,767
I came back!
I saved you!

876
01:19:57,903 --> 01:19:59,767
- Daddy! Daddy!
- Seth!

877
01:20:01,731 --> 01:20:03,905
Oh, God!

878
01:20:11,144 --> 01:20:12,767
Take him! Take him!

879
01:20:39,696 --> 01:20:42,216
Y-you should've
let me die.

880
01:20:47,662 --> 01:20:49,388
